# üé® Quick CSS Reference Guide\n\n## üìå Most Important Files\n\n### 1. `src/index.css` - Theme Variables\n```css\n:root {\n  /* Colors */\n  --color-bg-primary: #0f172a;\n  --color-text-primary: #e5e7eb;\n  --color-accent-cyan: #05adc1;\n  \n  /* Shadows */\n  --shadow-md: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);\n  --glow-cyan: 0 0 16px rgba(5, 172, 193, 0.3);\n  \n  /* Radius */\n  --radius-md: 12px;\n  --radius-lg: 16px;\n}\n```\n\n### 2. `src/App.css` - Layout Structure\n- Sidebar: fixed 260px width\n- Main content: flex with margin-left: 260px\n- Full-screen: min-height 100vh\n\n---\n\n## üéØ Copy-Paste Patterns\n\n### Glassy Card\n```css\n.my-card {\n  background: rgba(26, 37, 64, 0.4);\n  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n  border: var(--border-glass);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);\n}\n\n.my-card:hover {\n  border-color: var(--color-accent-cyan);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg), var(--glow-cyan);\n  transform: translateY(-4px);\n}\n```\n\n### Input Field\n```css\ninput {\n  background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4);\n  border: var(--border-glass);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-md);\n  color: var(--color-text-primary);\n  padding: 10px 12px;\n}\n\ninput:focus {\n  outline: none;\n  border-color: var(--color-accent-cyan);\n  box-shadow: var(--glow-cyan);\n}\n```\n\n### Button\n```css\n.btn {\n  background: var(--gradient-accent);\n  color: white;\n  border: none;\n  padding: 10px 16px;\n  border-radius: var(--radius-md);\n  cursor: pointer;\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);\n  transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.btn:hover {\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg), var(--glow-cyan-intense);\n  transform: translateY(-2px);\n}\n```\n\n### Full-Width Container\n```css\n.container {\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 100%;\n  padding: 40px 20px;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## üåà Color Usage\n\n| Purpose | Variable | Hex |\n|---------|----------|-----|\n| Main text | `--color-text-primary` | #e5e7eb |\n| Secondary text | `--color-text-secondary` | #d1d5db |\n| Muted text | `--color-text-muted` | #9ca3af |\n| Cyan accent | `--color-accent-cyan` | #05adc1 |\n| Blue accent | `--color-accent-blue` | #3b82f6 |\n\n---\n\n## üìè Spacing Rules\n\n```css\n/* Always use multiples of 8px */\nmargin: 8px;    /* Small gap */\nmargin: 16px;   /* Medium gap */\nmargin: 24px;   /* Large gap */\nmargin: 32px;   /* Extra large */\n```\n\n---\n\n## üîÑ Responsive Media Queries\n\n```css\n/* Desktop (1920px+) */\n@media (min-width: 1920px) {\n  .content { padding: 48px 32px; }\n}\n\n/* Laptop (1366px-1919px) */\n@media (min-width: 1366px) and (max-width: 1919px) {\n  .content { padding: 40px 24px; }\n}\n\n/* Tablet (768px-1024px) */\n@media (max-width: 1024px) {\n  .content { padding: 32px 20px; }\n}\n\n/* Mobile (<640px) */\n@media (max-width: 640px) {\n  .content { padding: 24px 16px; }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## ‚úÖ Checklist for New Components\n\n- [ ] Use `var(--color-*)` for all colors\n- [ ] Border radius: use `var(--radius-md/lg)`\n- [ ] Backgrounds: `rgba(26, 37, 64, 0.4)` for glass effect\n- [ ] Borders: use `var(--border-glass)`\n- [ ] Shadows: use `var(--shadow-md/lg)`\n- [ ] Hover: add `transform: translateY(-2px)`\n- [ ] Hover: add glow effect\n- [ ] Mobile: test at 640px, 768px\n- [ ] Accessibility: test focus states\n\n---\n\n## üé® Theme Customization\n\nTo change theme globally, update `:root` in `src/index.css`:\n\n```css\n:root {\n  --color-accent-cyan: #YOUR_COLOR_HERE;\n  /* All components auto-update! */\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## üìö Full Documentation\n\nSee `THEME_DOCUMENTATION.md` for complete reference\n\n---\n\n**Happy coding! üöÄ**\n